Class BasicRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.easyrules.core.BasicRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Rule>, Rule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicJmxRule, CompositeRule

    public class BasicRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements Rule, java.lang.Comparable<Rule>
    Basic rule implementation class that provides common methods. You can extend this class and override evaluate() and execute() to provide rule conditions and actions logic.
